#* {{zh-x|非 依 法定 程序 之 逮捕、拘禁、審問、處罰，得 拒絕 之。|Any arrest, detention, trial, or punishment which is not in accordance with the procedure prescribed by law '''can''' be resisted.|ref=Article 8, Constitution of the Republic of China (Taiwan)}}
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese}} to [[only]] [[have]]; to just have
#: {{zh-x|得 佢 想 去 公園{jyun4-2} 咋{zaa3}。|Only he wants to go to the park.|C}}
